# Design guidelines

Read `docs/DESIGN_GUIDELINES.md` before changing UI.

## Must follow

- Primary green `#2E7D32`, mint surfaces `#E1F2D9`, radial sage wash `#959F96` → `#E5E5E5`
- Soft rounded mint cards (16–20px), translucent landing CTAs, large circular mobile actions
- Flutter repo is **read-only visual/UX reference** — never copy architecture or Dart code
- Scoring registration is **by player name** (search/select), never QR
- Admin uses the same palette; confirm destructive actions
- No frontend score/handicap calculation; display backend values only
